1
00:00:21,280 --> 00:00:23,140
Why are you hiding here all alone?

2
00:00:30,680 --> 00:00:33,720
I can't stand that guy Su Cheng following you around all day.

3
00:00:33,720 --> 00:00:34,600
So,

4
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:37,640
out of sight, out of mind.

5
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:41,560
Are you jealous?

6
00:00:43,760 --> 00:00:45,920
Su Cheng saved my life.

7
00:00:47,040 --> 00:00:48,880
Once he is fully recovered,

8
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:51,210
I will explain everything to him clearly.

9
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:53,080
Okay.

10
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:54,640
I'll wait for you.

11
00:00:56,400 --> 00:00:59,920
Then we'll escape from this place of trouble,

12
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:02,320
and return to our Yuyun tree.

13
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,720
I advise you to leave Jiuyun.

14
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,039
Someone like you

15
00:01:23,039 --> 00:01:25,480
doesn't deserve to be with the one you love.

16
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:26,740
Don't you understand?

17
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,120
Love

18
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:31,039
can't be forced.

19
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,759
You can't give Ayun happiness.

20
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:36,479
The pill that saved you under the cliff

21
00:01:36,479 --> 00:01:38,140
was made by Mo Di at my request.

22
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,840
Its power is limited.

23
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:45,000
You have less than a year to live.

24
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:12,320
What's wrong? You look so serious.

25
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,280
It's nothing.

26
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:20,720
I was just thinking.

27
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,600
We've been through so much for the Pill Manual.

28
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,800
I wonder if there is a recipe in it

29
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:31,240
that can extend life.

30
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:35,079
This Pill Manual

31
00:02:35,079 --> 00:02:36,520
enhances power by overdrawing one's life.

32
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,160
How could it extend life?

33
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:40,240
It seems

34
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,960
I am destined to die soon.

35
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,520
What are your plans next?

36
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,520
Wherever you go,

37
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,760
I will follow you.

38
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:58,520
I'm just a shadow.

39
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,800
If you follow me,

40
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:02,410
I'm afraid you will suffer.

41
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:04,280
I will take good care of you.

42
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,840
I won't let you suffer.

43
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,440
If I can't be with you until the end,

44
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:09,800
will you regret it?

45
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:13,040
As long as we are together now, that's enough.

46
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,160
Yeah.

47
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:17,040
We'll find a small mountain village

48
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:19,250
and retire from the martial world.

49
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:21,200
We'll have a child or two

50
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:25,000
and live our peaceful little life.

51
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,560
Ayun.

52
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,120
I'm sorry.

53
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:32,120
I'm afraid this simple happiness

54
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:34,720
is something I can't even

55
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,760
give you right now.

56
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,600
If you truly care about Jiuyun,

57
00:03:57,880 --> 00:04:00,140
you should leave her as soon as possible.

58
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,760
Don't be so smug.

59
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,840
Even if I die,

60
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:07,360
I won't let you force Ayun.

61
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,690
A good bird chooses a fine tree to roost in.

62
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:11,400
She will understand this truth

63
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:13,120
sooner or later.

64
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:16,079
But if you dare to force Ayun,

65
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:17,839
even if I die,

66
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,880
I will take you down with me.

67
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:31,320
A'yu, come taste what I just made.

68
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,240
A'yun.

69
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:49,080
Getting to know you

70
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,480
and loving you

71
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,690
is the greatest fortune of my life.

72
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:54,680
I am just a shadow.

73
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:57,880
I don't know how to live for myself.

74
00:04:57,880 --> 00:05:00,210
And I'm afraid I can't give you happiness.

75
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:03,810
Perhaps leaving at the most beautiful moment

76
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,080
is good for both of us.

77
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,400
I hope you can forget me from now on.

78
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:11,720
Don't hate me for leaving without saying goodbye.

79
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,680
Because hate

80
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:15,840
will make me stay in your heart forever.

81
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,400
Someone like me

82
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,000
is not worth it.

83
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:27,040
Did you do something to force Mo Yu away?

84
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,840
You know Mo Yu's temperament best.

85
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,450
How could I force him with just a few words?

86
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,260
He left this jade pendant behind.

87
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:38,730
I'm afraid he is determined to forget about you completely.

88
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:51,880
You took great pains to save my life.

89
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:54,960
I'm afraid it wasn't for old times' sake.

90
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,800
You are wanted by both countries.

91
00:05:56,800 --> 00:06:00,400
Even if you get out, there is absolutely no chance for a comeback.

92
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:02,440
Did you come

93
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:05,880
just to tell me this?

94
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,280
But I can.

95
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:10,420
As long as you tell me the secret in the Pill Book.

96
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:16,040
You really are the good grandson I taught so carefully.

97
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:20,520
With your alchemy skills, you could have created an invincible army long ago.

98
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:22,440
But you haven't made a move.

99
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:24,560
Instead, you've been plotting to get the Pill Book.

100
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,290
There is only one possibility.

101
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:30,680
There's an even bigger secret hidden in the Pill Book.

102
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,760
Grandpa,

103
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,960
what exactly is this secret?

104
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:40,680
If I tell you the secret now,

105
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:44,520
I'm afraid I won't live past tonight.

106
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:05,040
This is a pill that gathers all the backlash injuries.

107
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,680
If you don't tell me,

108
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:10,640
I'll make you wish you were dead right now.

109
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:16,280
Although you are not my biological grandson,

110
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:20,320
you have learned my decisiveness and ruthlessness.

111
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,040
This Pill Book

112
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:27,080
was written by the emperor of the previous dynasty based on the Nine Palaces numerology.

113
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:29,010
The secret recipe in the Pill Book,

114
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:32,800
as long as it's arranged in the order of one, six,

115
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,560
seven, two,

116
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,480
nine, four,

117
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,400
three, eight,

118
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,560
and five,

119
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:44,680
can lead to the previous emperor's

120
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:47,520
treasure location.

121
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:54,480
I've told you

122
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,480
everything I know.

123
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:01,120
Give me a quick death.

124
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,920
I don't want to suffer this torture anymore.

125
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,400
You raised me for many years.

126
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,600
As for this small wish,

127
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,920
I can still grant it to you.

128
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,460
Baorui.

129
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:35,600
Pengyin.

130
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,730
Zijian Qiangqipin.

131
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:37,730
Quan Xuhang.

132
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,289
Quan Yulong.

133
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,580
Licheng Lefei.

134
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:41,480
Yunlong Yinyu Jia Guangjing.

135
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,140
Yunlong Yinyu Jia Guangjing.

136
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:45,640
Luo Xiaocong Lin Xunbo.

137
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:45,880
Luo Xiaocong Lin Xunbo.
